  "description": "This individual is a small goblin of notably ratlike proportions, defined by bright_green skin and a narrow, wedge-shaped face adapted to squeezing through crevices. Brown eyes sit deep under heavy brow ridges, and black hair is kept in an unkempt, sparse line along the crown that leaves the ears and scalp largely exposed. The incisors are prominent and uneven, and the nose bears permanent abrasions consistent with repeated contact against stone and timber. Limbs are wiry and long-fingered, ending in hard, darkened nails suited to scrabbling over wet rock and refuse.",
